<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome - Magnificat Central Credit Cooperative</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <style>
      body {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
      .card {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto 15px;
      }
      .card-body {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .justified-text {
        text-align: justify;
      }
      .left-aligned-list {
        text-align: left;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/mccc-reg-logo.png" alt="MCCC Logo" class="logo" />
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Welcome to the Registration Portal</h5>
        <p class="card-text justified-text">
          <strong
            >Please note, only Filipino Citizens who are 18 years old and above
            are eligible for an MCCC membership.</strong
          >
        </p>
        <!-- Membership Agreement Text -->
        <div class="mb-4">
          <p class="justified-text">
            I hereby apply for a membership with
            <strong>MAGNIFICAT CENTRAL CREDIT COOPERATIVE (MCCC)</strong>. I
            hereby agree to obey faithfully its rules and regulations as set
            down in its Articles of Incorporation and By-Laws, policies, and
            decisions of the general membership and those of the Board of
            Directors.
          </p>
          <p class="justified-text"><strong>I hereby pledge to:</strong></p>
          <ul class="left-aligned-list">
            <li>
              Attend and finish the prescribed Pre-Registration Seminar (PRS).
            </li>
            <li>
              Pay the one-time membership fee of <strong>Php500.00</strong>.
            </li>
            <li>Participate in the following program:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Subscribe for at least thirty (30) shares and pay at least 10
                shares (total value Php3,000.00) as stated in the terms and
                conditions prescribed in the Membership Agreement.
              </li>
              <li>
                Open a Savings Account (SA) with MCCC with an initial deposit of
                at least <strong>Php500.00</strong>.
              </li>
              <li>
                Participate in Continuous Capital Build-Up of
                <strong>Php100.00/month</strong>.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </ul>
          <p class="justified-text">
            Comply with the membership and subscription agreement.
          </p>
          <p class="justified-text">
            <strong
              >For your consideration, I do hereby include my Personal
              Data.</strong
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <form action="/start" method="POST">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 mt-3">
            Start Registration
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
